
  esperuino - sketch for arduino ATMega328.

It makes a Board computer from arduino using OBDI (ALDL) Car interface.

Hardware:

 - Arduino Nano V3.0 (ATMega328p)
 - LCD 20x4 character display module
 - 3-pin IR receiver (for Remote Control)
 - IR remote control (any spare, should be sniffed for codes)
 - npn transistor (for LCD backlight control)
 - L9637D ISO-to-Serial adapter chip
